data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
[Case: Soon Expiring] Hello, Your password expires very soon. It is unfortunately much possible you missed the notification balloon. Now you should change it. If not in the office, make sure you connect to the VPN. Initiate the password change by pushing the ctrl+alt+del keys simultaneously, and then click on Change a Password... A new password shall be between 8..12 chars, have a Uppercase, a Digit, a Special, no dictionnary word, nor previous parts. Once changed it will be valid for 3 months. Since an expired password is an annoyance for delocalized users especially, please book a reminder event in your outlook a week before it expires, just in case the balloon is missed.
ps: If you are logged with the Smartcard, you won't be able to reach the Change Password screen, so if in that case, please log off, remove the smartcard, log in again with the password. Then change it.
Thanks in advance. IT Operations
